flowchart LR
    ViT[ViT 2020<br/>patch tokens as visual sequence]
    DINO[DINO 2021<br/>self-distilled ViT features]
    IBOT[iBOT 2021<br/>masked patch self-distillation]
    CLIP[CLIP 2021<br/>image-text foundation features]
    OpenCLIP[OpenCLIP 2022<br/>open LAION-scale baseline]
    Data[LVD-142M 2023<br/>curated 142M image corpus]
    DINOv2[DINOv2 2023<br/>robust SSL visual backbone]
    Registers[ViT Registers 2023<br/>cleaner dense maps]
    Depth[Depth Anything 2024<br/>DINOv2-style depth teacher]
    DinoText[DINOv2 Meets Text 2024<br/>language-aligned dense features]
    Robotics[Robotics / 3D / remote sensing 2024+<br/>frozen geometry-rich backbone]
    Biology[Cell-DINO / XRay-DINO 2025<br/>domain-specific SSL backbones]

    ViT --> DINO
    DINO --> DINOv2
    IBOT --> DINOv2
    CLIP --> OpenCLIP
    OpenCLIP -.failure baseline for dense detail.-> DINOv2
    Data --> DINOv2
    DINOv2 --> Registers
    DINOv2 --> Depth
    DINOv2 --> DinoText
    DINOv2 --> Robotics
    DINOv2 --> Biology